Sentencas: Mixed ionic electronic conductor La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta in the porous form can be used as cathodes for solid oxide fuel cells and supports for thin oxygen separation membranes.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of porous La0.6Sr0.4C0.2Fe0.8O3-δ ceramics

Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8 O3-delta porous ceramics were prepared by solid state reaction.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of porous La0.6Sr0.4C0.2Fe0.8O3-δ ceramics

Sentencas: The porosity and pore size were investigated as a function of sintering temperature, molding pressure and amount of organic additive.
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of porous La0.6Sr0.4C0.2Fe0.8O3-δ ceramics

Sentencas: The experimental results show that with increasing porosity, its nitrogen permeability increases, but its electrical conductivity decreases as described by sigma = sigma (0).(1 - P)(3.1).
Titulo: Preparation and characterization of porous La0.6Sr0.4C0.2Fe0.8O3-δ ceramics
